column5: Fly in trip to Lake Herbert, northern quebec- 3rd week of July looking for 2-4 guys to round out trip- leaving from Allentown, PA - total cost est. $800 Good fishing for walleyes and pike - lots of fish and some nice trophies- if interested and more details email me at [email protected]
Sound good, I have to give guys credit who plan trips it is a tough job. Mike ( [email protected] )
